locs.text: yatajawaz miftah API almuhya fi al'iiedadat

nushje ealaa aliastikhdam almaswuwl la Chatbot. yustakhdam hadha wajihat barmajat tatbiqat ChatGPT, almamlukat lisharikat OpenAI. lasna tabiein laha, wahadha lays eamil ChatGPT rsmyan. nusi biqira'at shurut wa'ahkam ChatGPT qabl astikhdam Chatbot. yumknk alkhuruj biastikhdam '/exit'.
hadath khata fi wajihat barmajat tatbiqat Chatbot AI:
qad yusdr hadha Chatbot rdwdan ghayr daqiqatin, lidha tahaqaq min sihat almaelumati.
alwajihat al'akhirat laysat hadhih alwajihat lilfasl eanha.
aktub miftah wajihat barmajat tatbiqat li ChatGPT
lam yatima tawfir miftah wajihat barmajat altatbiqati.
yuhyy rubut aldardashat aldhakia aladhi yaemal binizam ChatGPT

miftah wajihat barmajat altatbiqat alkhasi bik la ChatGPT lilwusuli. yumkinuk astikhdam miftah wajihat barmajat altatbiqat almajani, walakin la yumkinuk astikhdam alnamadhij almutaqadimati. 'iidha kunt targhab fi alwusul alkamil 'iilaa jamie alnamadhij almadfueati, fasayataeayan ealayk aldafe muqabil alwusuli.
